essentiels (1 ou 2) meurent. On biaise la proportion en éliminant certains individus.

The underdominance construct is engineered to produce a lethal
toxin during early life stages, unless the individual also possesses
a copy of the other underdominance construct, which harbors a
suppressor for transcription of the toxin gene on the first construct.
[Davis] Success in engineering a single allele
-the heterozygote not viable while the two

Système ultra-simple, 1 locus. La toxine est

retombe si coût de fitness du drive.
